Somali pirates hijack a South Korean owned Kenyan registered fishing boat with 43 crew aboard. (Yonhap) (BBC)The United States Border Patrol finds a sophisticated tunnel between Tijuana in Mexico and Otay Mesa, California, used by drug smugglers. (Reuters)A court in Zambia grants bail to two Chinese managers accused of attempted murder for shooting and injuring 11 coal miners during a protest over pay and working conditions. (Reuters) (Zambian Watchdog)